Subject: drm/amdgpu: Enable gfxoff quirk on MacBook Pro
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 4593c1b6d159f1e5c35c07a7f125e79e5a864302
